                  </hi>. I am a widow, and am a baker. Between six and seven o'clock in the evening of the 18th of July I heard a knock at the till,—I came into the shop, and saw the prisoner coming from behind the till, which was open, and the bowl containing the money gone—there was from 26<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. to 30<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. gone—I am quite certain the prisoner is the person—he was overtaken, and 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. found on him—this is the bowl.</p>
